title: His Name is...
author: Oniii_Chan
pages:
#- His name is Pajeet,

And he’s out on the street,

He’s had quite a treat,

And his feet are quite beat.

#- He knows it is time,

But he can’t spare a dime,

As his poor guts;
 
Crackle and whine

#- As the sun shines,

He plops down a squat.

Here he prepares,
 
to end his despairs.

#- Coming all down,

to plop on the spot.

Here he shall drop,

That curry so hot.

#- The loo, so new

A luxury so far.

Even the paper,

To wipe up his caper.

#- A poem by Sheckles, not participating in civclassics.

October 24th, 2018
#- 